      <p>Our purpose at "Splash Falls" is to increase our profit by five percent with our new web site which is accessible to all and can be found on multiple devices. The boss and founder of this company is Logan Gilbert. He loves the outdoors, sports, and family and is excited to interact with adventurous people like him. He wants to make this a place where families, church groups, and friends can come enjoy themselves in the outdoors. Another goal is to increase revenue by ten percent by next year and to get the company's name out in the open. We wish to advertise hugely in the next couple months and especially during the summer.    </p>
    
    <h1>Important to know</h1>  
      <p>Our goal at "Splash Falls" is to have our customers leave   knowing they had an enjoyable time. A postive, friendly place where safety is our top priority. We wish to earn your trust as we assist you in your adventure down the river. The recommended age is between 12-65. You must be at least 4'5 and weigh more than 85 pounds to ride. Prices range from age to age. Under 12 is $150. Adults are $220. Life jacket are provided. Our website is accessable on mutiple devices including cell phones and PC's. Payments can also be made online. Water rafting is an amazing exerience and at "Splash Falls" we are here to make it unforgetable.</p>
  
